    arm64: dts: qcom: add early OnePlus 15 support

    Add a reduced Canoe device tree containing CPUs, PSCI, timer, GICv3, GCC, TLMM and the SE7 GENI debug UART.

    This is an early bring-up description. DRAM sizing remains bootloader-provided and the external GCC clock inputs are temporary fixed-clock placeholders.

